# IntelliMatch: AI Resume Screener

An AI-powered Resume Screening App that matches candidate resumes with job descriptions using **TF-IDF** similarity and a trained ML model.


## Features
- Upload Resume Dataset (CSV)
- Paste Job Description
- Calculates **TF-IDF Similarity**
- Predicts **Hire / Reject**
- Displays Top Candidates
- Downloadable Results in CSV



## Tech Stack
- **Python**
- **Streamlit**
- **Scikit-learn**
- **Pandas**
- **Joblib**



## Folder Structure
app/
└── streamlit_app.py
model/
├── tfidf_vectorizer.pkl
└── ai_recruiter_model.pkl
data/
└── AI_Resume_Screening.csv
requirements.txt
README.md



## ▶How to Run
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app/streamlit_app.py

